    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1847933174" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18247278687072440611">A long twisting tale of love and intrigue.<br/>Masterful story telling. Fun to read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


